# Completed Plans Archive

Plans that have reached 100% completion are logged here with timestamps and feature summaries.

## Format

Each entry contains:
- Plan ID and name
- Completion date/time
- Feature breakdown with completion times
- Total duration
- Notes (if any)

---

## Example Entry (to be auto-filled)

```
## Plan: Example Plan Name
- **ID:** example-plan-2026-04-22
- **Completed:** 2026-04-22 18:45:00
- **Duration:** 5 hours 30 minutes
- **Features Completed:**
  - ✅ Feature 1 (2 todos) — completed 2026-04-22 13:15
  - ✅ Feature 2 (3 todos) — completed 2026-04-22 15:30
  - ✅ Feature 3 (1 todo) — completed 2026-04-22 18:45
- **Notes:** Notable insights, gotchas, or follow-up items
```

---

*This file is auto-updated when plans reach 100% completion.*

